text.section:
Such program shall provide for:
Effective controls over the creation, maintenance, and use of records in the conduct of current business;
Cooperation with the department in applying standards, procedures, and techniques designed to improve the management of records;
Promotion of the maintenance and security of records deemed appropriate for preservation, and facilitation of the segregation and disposal of records of temporary value;
Compliance with the provisions of KRS 171.410 to 171.740 and the rules and regulations of the department; and
Compliance with the provisions of KRS 61.931 to 61.934.
